N2  - My assignment is to discuss mathematics in the management science of tomorrow. The preceding talks have dealt with potential uses by management of emerging and possible scientific developments. In approaching my assignment I would like to shift the emphasis slightly in order to discuss possible repercussions of a developing science of management on mathematics as well as possible repercussions of mathematical developments for the science of management.
